00:00:16.083 --> 00:00:17.458
<i>Sweetheart.</i>

3
00:00:19.416 --> 00:00:20.416
Darling.

4
00:00:29.958 --> 00:00:31.666
Someone's going home?

5
00:00:32.250 --> 00:00:33.330
What are you talking about?

6
00:00:33.791 --> 00:00:36.500
